    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/c8e16d4c3378fa88d6838481c0da7c17.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=118 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/9ddc9416254ac8268088a4b6a5f8e7d2.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=134 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/265e70c24b8b396ee851bb238dce0bff.webp?t=1770568536\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/265e70c24b8b396ee851bb238dce0bff.poster.avif?t=1770568536\" class=\"bb_img\" width=607 height=337 /></picture></span>踏上穿越世界树Yggdrasill所延伸出的九大国度的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从壮丽的世界到黑暗的深渊，每个国度都充满了独特的氛围、危险与特色。与巨人作战，在冰封迷宫中求生，净化魔法森林。每个国度都有自己的节奏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/f0668f0a59dbf69231b1c5f2567c686e.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=80 /></span>每一次出发，都会踏上全新的道路。探索神秘的地牢，使用捷径，自定义你的旅程。难度由你决定。你是选择轻松之路，还是挑战不断升级的困难，追逐更高的奖励并敢于对抗洛基？通过永久强化和动态成长系统，你将一次次变得更强大。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/0ac94ec12d270937251672392d8a86e4.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=80 /></span>与你熟悉的角色建立深厚羁绊，如索尔、芙蕾雅、海姆达尔和艾崔，同时面对黑暗而传奇的敌人。你与每位角色的互动将塑造你的故事，让你置身于充满盟友支持与敌人怒火的史诗之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/a138546581c212368cf816785f642aff.webp?t=1770568536\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/a138546581c212368cf816785f642aff.poster.avif?t=1770568536\" class=\"bb_img\" width=609 height=194 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/7ddd5aea58f8ff77454b8c9bfdcbfba3.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过获取武器、技能和神之祝福来增强实力。将提尔的正义之矛与芙蕾雅的幻影伏击等力量结合，打造属于你的战斗风格。创造独特组合，在每次战斗中爆发更强力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/3b736f5513aa14f6ba5311fb9dd2849f.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Ragnar》将根据玩家的反馈持续开发。每次更新都会加入新角色、武器、机制和故事内容，使游戏世界更加丰富和深刻。我们重视你的意见，因此游戏将以抢先体验的形式开启，并与玩家一同走向完整版本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309140/extras/10a5c34c5eee0b0b3d9ca1d2c89a2906.avif?t=1770568536\" width=607 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阻止洛基在诸神黄昏中引发的混乱，在北欧神话最黑暗的时刻中，推翻他的王座，成为照亮世界的光芒。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 土耳其语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 日语, 韩语, 俄语, 瑞典语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
